<%= provide(:title, sanitize(@post.title)) %>

<%= render 'partials/blog_twitter_cards' %>

<div class="header-container">
  <nav class="nav padding-vertical-large center">
    <div class="site-title">
      <%= link_to "The Zen Woods", root_url %>
    </div>
    <div class="padding-top-mini">
      Stress-free productivity.
    </div>
  </nav>
</div>

<div class="padding-bottom">
  <div class="product-title-background">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="post-title white-text right padding-vertical">
        <%= @post.title %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="container">

  <div class="padding-bottom center">
    Posted on <%= @post.created_at.strftime("%m.%d.%Y") %> | <%= @post.readtime %> minute read | <%= @post.element %>
  </div>

  <div class="image-container">
    <img class="large-image" src="<%= @post.image %>" width="100%" />
    <div class="bottom-left">
      <%= @post.image_credit %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sub-title center padding-vertical-large">
    <%= @post.tagline %>
  </div>

</div>


<div class="container">
  <div class="flex">

    <div class="seventy">
      <div class="best">
        <%= sanitize(@post.content) %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="padding-vertical-large container">
  <div class="flex">
    <div class="seventy">

      <div class="sub-title padding-bottom">
        I want people to know about this!
      </div>

      <div class="padding-bottom">
        The more people willing to learn about our environment, the better our world will be. You're already making a difference, let's help your friends make a difference too! Choose your blue.
      </div>

      <div class="flex">
        <div class="fifty">
          <a onclick="javascript:window.open('https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=<%= post_url(@post) %>', '_blank', 'width=800, height=500, top=200, left=300');void(0)" class="facebook-button">Facebook</a>
        </div>

        <div class="fifty">
          <a onclick="javascript:window.open('https://twitter.com/share?text=<%= @post.title %> - &amp;url=<%= post_url(@post) %>', '_blank', 'width=800, height=500, top=200, left=300');void(0)" class="twitter-button">Twitter</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="padding-vertical element-background">
  <div class="container">
    
    <div class="image-container">
      <img class="large-image" src="<%= @post.image_bottom %>" width="100%" />
      <div class="bottom-left">
        <%= @post.image_bottom_credit %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="padding-vertical-large container">
  <div class="flex">
    <div class="seventy">

      <div class="sub-title padding-bottom">
        Thanks for reading this far!
      </div>

      <div class="padding-bottom">
        We really do appreciate it! You must be pretty serious about helping out the planet if you just read an entire post for fun. Let's take it one step further. Enter your email below, and we will help you help the Earth now and in the future! (pssst... it's free!)
      </div>

      <span class="email_form_post"><%= render 'partials/emails/email_form_post' %></span>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="padding-bottom-large container">
  <div class="flex">
    <div class="seventy">

      <% @recent_posts.each do |post| %>
        <div class="sub-title padding-bottom">
          <%= link_to post.title, post_path(post), class: "home-post-link" %>
        </div>

        <img class="large-image" src="<%= post.image_bottom %>" width="100%" />

        <div class="padding-vertical">
          <%= post.tagline %>
        </div>

        <div class="padding-bottom-large">
          <%= link_to post_path(post) do %>
            <div class="more-button">
              Read more...
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="sub-title center padding-bottom-large">
        <%= link_to "View more posts...", posts_path %>
      </div>

      <div class="sub-title padding-bottom">
        What else can you do to make life better?
      </div>

      <div class="padding-bottom">
        Even the simpliest, easiest things can help make your life the best. Enter your email below, and we will help you now and in the future! (pssst... it's free!)
      </div>

      <span class="email_form_post"><%= render 'partials/emails/email_form_post' %></span>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>